WEBVTT

00:01.430 --> 00:02.419
- YAAY! YAAY!

00:02.470 --> 00:04.062
- JULIET...

00:04.100 --> 00:05.397
JULIET?

00:05.430 --> 00:08.433
[kids laughing]

00:11.570 --> 00:14.505
JULIET,
PARTY'S ALMOST OVER.

00:14.540 --> 00:16.804
I DON'T THINK
DADDY'S COMING, SWEETIE.

00:16.850 --> 00:18.545
- HE'S COMING,
I KNOW IT.

00:18.580 --> 00:20.116
- OKAY.

00:20.150 --> 00:22.482
BUT IT'S A LITTLE RUDE
TO STAY IN HERE ALL DAY.

00:22.520 --> 00:24.442
AND HEY, YOUR CLOWN'S
LEAVING SOON.

00:24.490 --> 00:26.287
- HE CAN'T EVEl_\l JUGGLE.
